CFG
Class Instruction

java.lang.Object
  CFG.Instruction

public class Instruction
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents each instruction line in the bytecode. It contains the type of instruction, the operation code, paramenters, line number in bytecode, and destination (if applicable).
